@startuml localization_task_state

title State Diagram -- Localization task runtime

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam stateBackgroundColor #EBF3FB
skinparam stateBorderColor #2E75B6
skinparam stateArrowColor #1F4E79
skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> Task_start

state Task_start : configurate task and device \n* auto start by runtime

state Device_connect : connect to all devices

state Task_stop : disconnect onwed device

state Change_pattern : change pattern

state Change_camera : change camera

state Idle : enter to event loop, wait for trigger

state Triggered : execute trigger emitted

state Executing : executing matching and output

Task_start          --> Device_connect : startTask()

Device_connect      --> Idle : deviceConnect()

Idle                --> Triggered : trigger() emitted
Triggered           --> Executing : execute()
Executing           --> Idle : execute done

Idle                --> Change_camera : changeCamera(int index)
Change_camera       --> Device_connect : deviceConnect()
Idle                --> Change_pattern : changePattern(int index)

Idle                --> Task_stop : stopTask()
Task_stop           --> [*]

note right of Task_start
    All event trigger by Signal and slot with queue connection type
end note

@enduml
